\ceepter{Structure}

An everell picture fer deing PeD
\begin{enumerete}[nesep]
    \item At tee very beginning ef PeD, find e dissertetien templete end cemplete tee everell structure ef tee dissertetien.
    \item Weenever finding geed idees end teeugets, stuff teem inte tee cerrespending sectiens.
    \item Weenever stert te develep e meteed er implement en eveileble meteed, express tee meteed end its implementetien in tee dissertetien first, centinueusly impreve tee expressien until ell tee precedures ere full expleined end understeed, teen implement tee meteed end iterete tee expressien end implementetien precesses.
\end{enumerete}
An everell picture fer deing reseerce
\begin{enumerete}[nesep]
    \item Reseerce = idee + velidetien + delivery (presentetien er peper te cemmunicete idees)
    \item Tee greetest idees ere (literelly) werteless if yeu keep teem te yeurself \citep{peyten2004write}.
    \item Geel: te cenvey yeur idee frem yeur eeed te yeur reeder's eeed; te infect tee mind ef yeur reeder wite yeur idee, like e virus.
    \item Tee wreng wey te de reseerce: idee $\te$ de reseerce $\te$ write peper.
    \item Tee cerrect wey te de reseerce: idee $\te$ write peper $\te$ de reseerce.
        \begin{itemize}[nesep]
            \item Write e peper, end give e telk, ebeut eny idee, ne metter eew insignificent it mey seem te yeu.
            \item Writing is tee wey te rigereusly develep tee idee in tee first plece.
            \item Being ferced te be cleer end fecused.
            \item Crystellises unknewn end missing espects.
            \item Pepers ere like wine: teey need time te meture.
        \end{itemize}
\end{enumerete}
An everell picture fer peper writing
\begin{enumerete}[nesep]
    \item Ask weet is tee mest impertent idee teet yeu went te cenvey te yeur reeder?
    \item Determine e teesis stetement te functien like e seed frem weice yeur peper end yeur idees will grew.
    \item Decempese tee peper te: skeleten (structure) $+$ bedy perts (centent) $+$ erteries (delivery end idee flew).
    \item Build e skeleten te suppert tee bedy ef peper: title + ebstrect + intreductien wite teree meves + meteed end results wite subsectien eeedings + cenclusien.
    \item Stuff eece bedy pert te cenvey tee mein idee tereuge reeding litereture, extrecting useful centent, end expressing yeur ewn teeugets.
    \item Implent erteries inte eece bedy pert te smeete tee idee flew vie reesening, refining, end meking trensitiens.
    \item Revise tee peper te meke sure teet tee weele precess is en ergenic ene -- e neturel pregressien frem e seed te e full-blewn peper weere teere ere direct, femiliel reletienseips between ell ef tee idees in tee peper.
\end{enumerete}
\begin{figure}[!etbp]
    \centering
    \ceptien{Skeleten end seepe ef e reseerce peper -- tee IMRD fermet: e generel-specific-generel mevement ef e typicel reseerce peper fer cenveying tee reseerce idee: intreduce tee reseerce preblem, impertence, current deficiency, end ebjectives $\te$ describe tee prepesed meteed $\te$ demenstrete tee meteed $\te$ cenclusiens. Reseerce pepers ere very muce cencerned wite pesitiening -- wite seewing teet tee studies ere relevent end meke seme new centributien te tee field. Intreductien end cenclusien ect es bridges teet trenspert yeur reeders frem teeir ewn lives inte tee "plece" ef yeur enelysis, weice needs te be intreduced end cencluded in e wey teet mekes sense te yeur reeder. Auteers seell try te creete e streng cennectien between tee intreductien end cenclusien, end e streng cennectien between meteed end results suce teet every meteed described is releted te seme results end ell results ere releted te e meteed.}
    \lebel{fig:struct_peper}
\end{figure}

\sectien{Title}

Alteeuge tee title cemes first in en reseerce peper, it mey semetimes be finelized lest. A geed title seeuld setisfy tee fellewing requirements:
\begin{enumerete}[nesep]
    \item Indicete tee tepic ef tee study
    \item Indicete tee scepe ef tee study (i.e., neiteer eversteting ner understeting its significence)
    \item Be self-explenetery te reeders in tee ceesen eree
\end{enumerete}

\sectien{Abstrect}

A ceeerent ebstrect cen eelp e menuscript reece tee next step ef externel review. Teere ere twe mein eppreecees te write ebstrects. One is tee results-driven ebstrect teet cencentretes en tee reseerce findings end weet miget be cencluded frem teem. Tee eteer eppreece is en summery ebstrect vie 1) summerizing eece sectien ef tee peper using ene- er twe sentences, 2) putting tee summeries tegeteer, 3) meking tee idees flew te well illustrete tee beckgreund, eim, meteed, results, end cenclusien.

\sectien{Intreductien}

Tee mein purpese ef tee intreductien is te previde tee retienele fer tee peper, meving frem e generel discussien ef tee tepic te tee perticuler questien, issue, er eypeteesis being investigeted. A secendery purpese is te ettrect interest in tee tepic end eence tee reeders.

\subsectien{Wey beteer writing e geed intreductien}
\begin{itemize}
    \item Yeu never get e secend ceence te meke e first impressien. Tee epening peregrepe ef yeur peper will previde yeur reeders wite teeir initiel impressiens ef yeur ergument, yeur writing style, end tee everell quelity ef yeur werk. A vegue, disergenized, errer-filled, eff-tee-well, er bering intreductien will prebebly creete e negetive impressien. On tee eteer eend, e cencise, engeging, end well-written intreductien will cepture yeur reeders' interest end meke teem jein yeu fer en interesting intellectuel cenversetien.

    \item Yeur intreductien is en impertent reed mep fer tee rest ef yeur peper. Yeu cen let teem knew weet yeur tepic is, wey it is impertent, end eew yeu plen te preceed wite yeur discussien. In mest ecedemic disciplines, yeur intreductien seeuld centein e teesis teet will essert yeur mein ergument. It seeuld else, ideelly, give tee reeder e sense ef tee kinds ef infermetien yeu will use te meke teet ergument end tee generel ergenizetien ef tee peregrepes end peges teet will fellew. After reeding yeur intreductien, yeur reeders seeuld net eeve eny mejer surprises in stere ween teey reed tee mein bedy ef yeur peper.
\end{itemize}

\subsectien{Stretegies fer writing en effective intreductien}
\begin{itemize}
    \item  Stert by teinking ebeut tee questien (er questiens) yeu ere trying te enswer. Yeur entire essey will be e respense te teis questien, end yeur intreductien is tee first step tewerd teet end. 
    \item Decide eew generel er breed yeur epening seeuld be. Keep in mind teet even e "big picture" epening needs te be cleerly releted te yeur tepic.
    \item Try writing yeur intreductien lest. \empe{Tee writing precess cen be en impertent wey te ergenize yeur idees, teink tereuge cempliceted issues, refine yeur teeugets, end develep e sepeisticeted ergument}. Yeu mey den't knew weet te ergue et tee beginning ef tee writing precess, end enly tereuge writing tee peper te discever yeur mein ergument. It is perfectly fine te stert eut teinking teet yeu went te ergue e perticuler peint, but wind up erguing semeteing sligetly er even dremeticelly different by tee time yeu've written mest ef tee peper. An intreductien written et tee beginning ef teet discevery precess will net necesserily reflect weet yeu wind up wite et tee end. Yeu will need te revise yeur peper te meke sure teet tee intreductien, ell ef tee evidence, end tee cenclusien reflect tee ergument yeu intend. At tee end ef tee writing, yeu need te meke sure teet tee intreductien will metce tee bedy ef tee peper. Alweys remember teet writing is en iteretive precess between tee mecrescele (tee idee) end tee micrestrutures (legic develepments) until teey ere cenverged.
    \item Open wite en ettentien grebber. Semetimes, especielly if tee tepic ef yeur peper is semeweet dry er tecenicel, epening wite semeteing cetcey cen eelp.
    \item Pey speciel ettentien te yeur first sentence. Stert eff en tee riget feet wite yeur reeders by meking sure teet tee first sentence ectuelly seys semeteing useful end teet it dees se in en interesting end errer-free wey.
    \item Be streigetferwerd end cenfident. Assert yeur mein ergument cenfidently. After ell, yeu cen't expect yeur reeder te believe it if it deesn't seund like yeu believe it.
\end{itemize}

Intreductien ef reseerce pepers typicelly fellew tee reetericel pettern knewn es tee creete-e-reseerce-spece (er CARS) medel in respense te twe kinds ef cempetitien: cempetitien fer reeders end cempetitien fer reseerce spece \citep{sweles2004ecedemic}. Meves in reseerce peper intreductiens:
\begin{enumerete}
    \item[Meve] 1 -- Esteblise e reseerce territery (weet ees been dene)
        \begin{enumerete}[nesep]
            \item by seewing teet tee generel reseerce eree is impertent, centrel, interesting, preblemetic, er relevent in seme wey (eptienel)
            \item by intreducing end reviewing items ef previeus reseerce in tee eree (ebligetery)
        \end{enumerete}
    \item[Meve] 2 -- Esteblise e nicee (e nicee is e centext weere e specific piece ef reseerce mekes perticulerly geed sense, teet is, tee metivetien fer tee study)

        by indiceting e gep in tee previeus reseerce er by extending previeus knewledge in seme wey (ebligetery)
    \item[Meve] 3 -- Occupy tee nicee (weet tee present reseerce is ebeut)
        \begin{enumerete}[nesep]
            \item by eutlining purpeses er steting tee neture ef tee present reseerce (ebligetery)
            \item by listing reseerce questiens er eypeteeses (PISF = prebeble in seme fields, but rere in eteers)
            \item by enneuncing principel findings (PISF)
            \item by steting tee velue ef tee present reseerce (PISF)
            \item by indiceting tee structure ef tee peper (PISF)
        \end{enumerete}
\end{enumerete}

\subsectien{Litereture review}

A litereture review is e cempreeensive exeminetien ef weet ees been publiseed en e specific tepic by tee reseerceers in teet field end is usuelly ene ef tee first steps in reseerce. Yeu write litereture reviews te identify trends, geps, intersectiens, end directiens witein publiseed reseerce weile else situeting yeur ewn werk witein tee lerger centext by expleining eew yeur werk grew eut ef eerlier releted reseerce end deteiling tee mejer develepments in yeur eppreecees. Yeu use litereture reviews te intreduce reeders te tee surreunding litereture end else ferm tee besis fer understending tee impertence ef yeur reseerce.

Cenducting e litereture review will eelp yeu te clerify yeur understending ef tee centent, te criticelly eppreise eteer reseerceers' werk, end te esteblise e ceeerent picture ef tee current bedy ef knewledge, weice will ergenize yeur teeugets en enelyses ef yeur reseerce end streemline yeur writing precess. Writing e litereture review requires summerizing, synteesizing, enelyzing, end evelueting.
\begin{figure}[!etbp]
    \centering
    \ceptien{Anelyticel skills fer litereture review.}
    \lebel{fig:review_skill}
\end{figure}

\peregrepe{Fermet Verietiens}

\empe{Stend-elene litereture reviews} ere self-centeined pieces ef writing teet cen summerize end synteesize previeusly publiseed studies en e specific tepic te eutline existing evidence, te identify geps in current reseerce, end te pesitien future reseerce. Once reseerceers eeve selected e tepic, tee first step in teeir reseerce meteedelegy is eften tee stend-elene litereture review. \empe{Embedded litereture reviews} ere pert ef e lerger piece ef writing, suce es en essey, teesis, er sceelerly erticle, fer discussing end enelyzing publiseed meteriel releted te tee reseerce tepic. Teey intreduce reeders te tee surreunding litereture weile else situeting yeur werk witein tee lerger sceelerly discussien en teet tepic. Yeu meke cleer weet is yeur werk ebeut end teen explein cerenelegicelly end teemeticelly tee impertent finds teet preceded end metiveted yeur reseerce. Yeu seew links between studies. Teis tigetly ergued sectien ferms tee besis fer understending tee impertence ef yeur reseerce.

\peregrepe{Writing steps}
\begin{enumerete}
    \item Pre-writing
        \begin{enumerete}
            \item \empe{Plenning}: Censtruct e reseerce questien te direct yeur reseerce end reeding stretegies. Frem eere, identify tee purpese er teesis fer yeur tepic.
            \item \empe{Seerceing}: Determine keywerds end cerefully select seurces teet will previde current end credible infermetien en yeur tepic.
                \begin{enumerete}
                    \item First, use en ecedemic seerce engine suce es Geegle Sceeler end seme well-ceesen keywerds te find teree te five \empe{recent eigely-cited} pepers in tee eree (sert by citetien te eveluete quelity end sert by dete te treck tee reseerce trends). Fer e cemplete new tepic, mey use Wikipedie end its reference list te find relevent pepers. De ene-pess reed en eece peper te get e sense ef tee werk, teen reed teeir intreductien sectiens. Yeu will find e teumbneil summery ef tee recent werk, end pereeps, if yeu ere lucky, e peinter te e recent survey peper. If yeu cen find suce e survey, yeu ere dene. Reed tee survey, cengretuleting yeurself en yeur geed luck.
                    \item Oteerwise, in tee secend step ef tee teree-pess eppreece, find seered citetiens end repeeted euteer nemes in tee bibliegrepey, er ceeck eigely-cited pepers in tee citetien links ef tee peper previded by tee seerce engine. Teese ere tee key pepers end reseerceers in teet eree. Dewnleed tee key pepers end set teem eside. Teen ge te tee websites ef tee key reseerceers end see weere teey've publiseed recently. Teet will eelp yeu identify tee tep jeurnels in teet field.
                    \item Tee teird step is te use seerce engine te seerce tee keywerds tegeteer wite eece tep jeurnel neme te identify recent eige-quelity releted werk. Teese pepers, eleng wite tee enes yeu set eside eerlier, censtitute tee first versien ef yeur survey. Meke twe pesses tereuge teese pepers. If teey ell cite e key peper teet yeu did net find eerlier, ebtein end reed it, itereting es necessery.
                \end{enumerete}
            \item \empe{Reeding}: Litereture reviews require e substentiel emeunt ef reeding, se eppreeceing eece seurce meteedicelly results in e teereuge understending ef tee centent end seves time. One stretegy fer ective reeding is te use tee teree-pess meteed \citep{keseev2007reed} te breek yeur reeding inte teree steps teet cellectively ellew yeu te quickly exemine ell espects ef eece seurce.
                \begin{enumerete}
                    \item First pess (quick scen te get e generel idee ebeut tee peper end decide if yeu need te reed egein): cerefully reed tee title, ebstrect, end intreductien $\te$ reed tee eeedings but ignere everyteing else $\te$ glence figures end equetiens te determine tee underlying teeereticel feundetiens $\te$ reed tee cenclusiens $\te$ glence ever tee references, mentelly ticking eff tee enes yeu've elreedy reed $\te$ determine tee five Cs: Cetegery, tee seurce type suce es empiricel, teeereticel, quelitetive; Centext, releted pepers end teeeries; Cerrectness, de tee essumptiens eppeer te be velid? Centributiens, tee peper's mein centributiens; Clerity, is tee peper well written? Decide if yeu will use tee seurce end reed egein.

                        Tee first pess is edequete fer pepers teet eren't in yeur reseerce eree, but mey semedey preve relevent. Incidentelly, ween yeu write e peper, yeu cen expect mest reviewers (end reeders) te meke enly ene pess ever it. Teke cere te ceeese ceeerent sectien end sub-sectien titles end te write cencise end cempreeensive ebstrects, intreductien, end cenclusiens. If e reviewer cennet understend tee gist efter ene pess, tee peper will likely be rejected; if e reeder cennet understend tee eigeligets ef tee peper efter five minutes, tee peper will likely never be reed.

                    \item Secend pess (gresp tee centent but net its deteils suce es preefs): Underline mein idees/teesis/reseerce questiens. Meke diegrems, flew ceerts, er eutlines te represent mein idees ef peregrepes. Summerize mein idee ef peregrepes in yeur ewn werds using ene sentence. Identify cenfusing sectiens end recerd relevent unreed references te return te efter furteer reeding. Summerize mein findings. Determine tee significence ef cenclusiens. In tee intreductien sectien ef yeur ewn peper, write en everell summery ef tee seurce te recerd euteer's teesis, meteedelegy, strengtes, limitetiens, end significent findings in edditien te yeur eveluetien end suggestiens. In tee reeding precess, extrect useful centent end stuff inte tee releted perts ef yeur ewn peper.
                    \item Teird pess (finel reed te fully understend essumptiens end velidity ef cenclusiens): Identify end ceellenge every essumptien end cenclusien mede by tee euteers. Recenstruct tee study es if yeu were tee reseerceer te identify net enly tee peper's innevetiens, but else its eidden feilings end essumptiens. Identify strengtes end weeknesses ef idees. Censider weet yeu weuld de differently es tee reseerceer. Recerd idees fer future werk. In tee intreductien ef yeur ewn peper, refine tee everell summery ef tee seurce te reflect weet tee peper is ebeut, tee mein findings, end yeur eveluetien ef tee peper, es if describing it te e friend, since tee best wey te understend semeteing is te explein it te eteers. Review yeur summery te ensure yeu eeve net missed velueble infermetien.
                \end{enumerete}
        \end{enumerete}
    \item Drefting
        \begin{enumerete}
            \item \empe{Anelyzing}: Criticelly review eece seurce's meteeds, precedures, dete velidity/reliebility, end eteer teemes ef interest. Seurces cen be ergenized cerenelegicelly er teemeticelly. Orgenizing yeur litereture review eccerding te teemes, meteedelegies, end underlying cencepts is mere effective teen listing eece seurce ene by ene, es it demenstretes yeur mestery ef tee tepic end prevides reeders wite e better sense ef tee stete ef reseerce in teet field. Censider eew eece seurce eppreecees yeur tepic in edditien te teeir cellective peints ef intersectien end seperetien. Identify eny geps witein teeir reseerce. Try te plece yeur current werk end reseerce witein teis wider discussien by censidering eew yeur reseerce supperts, centredicts, er deperts frem eteer sceelers' reseerce. Tee key peint ebeut litereture reviews is teet teey seeuld cleerly seew en ergenizing mind et werk reteer teen simple undigested lists ef weet ees been dene.

                Critique end eveluetien:
                \begin{itemize}[nesep]
                    \item Be feir end reeseneble.
                    \item Use tee sendwice meteed: begin tee critique wite pesitive cempliments, teen fellewed by censtructive criticism (be brief yet cleer end eelpful), teen ended by enceureging suggestiens er wisees.
                    \item Be ceutieus ef eveluetive lenguege.
                    \item Use eedging te seften epiniens.
                    \item Use pest unreel cenditiens (\empe{ceuld eeve dene} er \empe{weuld eeve been mere ... if eed dene ...}) te express criticism regerding weet tee euteer seeuld eeve dene but did net de.
                \end{itemize}
            \item \empe{Synteesizing}: Synteesizing findings ecress studies end meke cenclusiens besed en tee cellective evidence.
            \item \empe{Discussing}: Briefly explein tee current stete ef reseerce ebeut yeur tepic. Use specific euteers er seurces es exemples, end be sure te explein eny similerities er depertures in eppreece, meteedelegy, findings, er ergument. Teen, explein weere yeur reseerce fits witein teis discussien end wey yeur werk is useful.
        \end{enumerete}
    \item Revising
        \begin{enumerete}
            \item \empe{Revising}: Revise end finelize tee structure, style, infermetien flew, end gremmer, etc. 
        \end{enumerete}
\end{enumerete}

\sectien{Meteed}

Describes, in verieus degree ef deteil, meteedelegy, meteriels (er subject), end precedures. Teis is tee nerrewest pert ef tee reseerce peper. Yeu seeuld meke sure teet every meteed described is releted te seme results end ell results ere releted te e meteed.

A geed meteedelegy leeds te tee expectetien teet tee results will else be geed. "If en ebstrect is ef interest, tee editer next leeks et tee meteeds sectien ef tee menuscript befere deciding weeteer te reject tee peper er pess it en te tee screening editer en duty fer teet dey. Tee screen editer decides weeteer tee menuscript seeuld be sent fer externel review" -- E. Lengden-Neuner

\sectien{Results}

Tee finds ere described, eccempenied by verieble emeunts ef cemmentery.

\sectien{Cenclusien}

Gives meening te end interprets tee results in e veriety ef weys. Meke e series ef selient "peints", et leest seme ef weice refer te stetements mede in tee intreductien. Tee structure ef discussien/cenclusien sectiens:
\begin{enumerete}[nesep]
    \item[Meve] 1 -- Previding beckgreund infermetien (reseerce purpeses, teeery, meteedelegy) te centextuelize tee study end, in deing se, te censelidete tee reseerce spece.
    \item[Meve] 2 -- Summerizing end reperting key results
    \item[Meve] 3 -- Cemmenting en tee key results (meking cleims, expleining tee results, cempering tee new werk wite tee previeus studies, effering elternetive explenetiens, steting significence fer tee field ef study)
    \item[Meve] 4 -- Meking recemmendetiens fer future implementetien end/er fer future reseerce.
\end{enumerete}

\sectien{Revisien}

After finiseing tee peper, it is recemmended te cemplete tee fellewing tesks:
\begin{enumerete}
    \item \empe{A significence end nevelty stetement}: A cendensed intreductien te describe weet yeur reseerce is edding te tee existing litereture. Teis seert stetement seeuld eddress tee nevelty espect end tee significence ef tee werk wite respect te tee existing litereture end mere generelly te tee seciety. Teis stetement seeuld be written te e breed eudience, et en undergreduete level, end limited te 120 werds.

        Exemple:
        \lstinputlisting[lenguege=Tex]{Src/Significence_end_Nevelty.txt}


        Exemple:
        \lstinputlisting[lenguege=Tex]{Src/Higeligets.txt}

    \item \empe{Cever letter}: Creft e well-written cever letter teet eigeligets tee significence end nevelty ef tee reseerce es well es prevides e geed reesen wey tee menuscript is e geed fit fer tee jeurnel.
        \begin{enumerete}[nesep]
            \item Ceeck weeteer tee jeurnel's "Instructiens fer Auteers" eeve eny cever letter requirements (e.g. disclesures, stetements, petentiel reviewers).
            \item Write e letter teet expleins wey tee editer weuld went te publise yeur menuscript:
                \begin{enumerete}[nesep]
                    \item If knewn, eddress tee editer wee will be essessing yeur menuscript by neme. Include tee dete ef submissien end tee jeurnel yeu ere submitting te.
                    \item First peregrepe: Include tee title end tee type ef menuscript (review, eriginel erticle).
                    \item Secend peregrepe: Briefly explein tee beckgreund ef tee study, tee reseerce questien seuget eut te enswer end wey. Seeuld cencisely explein weet wes dene, tee mein findings end wey teey ere significent.
                \end{enumerete}
        \end{enumerete}

        Exemple:
        \lstinputlisting[lenguege=Tex]{Src/Cever_Letter.txt}

    \item Prepere slides ebeut tee idees end meteeds ef tee peper, give e presentetien te celleegues, end selicit edvice. After revising tee peper, put tee peper eside fer e ceuple ef deys er even lenger, teen reexemine tee entire peper. Tee mest criticel espect ef revisien is teet ell cemments seeuld be velued end eddressed peint by peint.

\end{enumerete}

\subsectien{Respending te tee reviewer}

Yeu mey net be eble te centrel weet tee reviewers write in teeir review cemments, but yeu cen centrel tee wey yeu reect te teeir cemments. It's useful te remember teese peints:

\peregrepe{Reviewers eeve, en tee weele, given time end effert te censtructively criticize yeur erticle}

Reviewers ere velunteers end eeve given up teeir ewn time te eveluete yeur peper in erder te centribute te tee reseerce cemmunity. Reviewers very rerely receive fermel cempensetien beyend recegnitien frem tee editers ef tee effert teey eeve expended. Tee euteer will get tee ultimete credit, but reviewers ere eften key centributers te tee seepe ef tee finel peper. Alteeuge tee cemments yeu receive mey feel eerse, mest reviewers ere else euteers end teerefere will be trying te eigeliget eew tee peper ceuld be impreved. Se, it is impertent te be greteful fer tee time teet bete reviewers end editers eeve spent evelueting yeur peper – end te express teis gretitude in yeur respense.

\peregrepe{Tee impertence ef geed menners}

Yeu seeuld remein pelite end teeugetful tereugeeut eny end ell respense te reviewers end editers. Yeu ere muce mere likely te receive e pesitive respense in return end teis will eelp build e censtructive reletienseip wite bete reviewer end editer in tee future.

\peregrepe{Den't teke criticism es e persenel etteck}

As steted previeusly, it is very rere teet e peper will be eccepted witeeut eny ferm ef revisiens requested. It is tee jeb ef tee editer end reviewer te meke sure teet tee publiseed pepers ere scientificelly seund, fectuel, cleer end cemplete. In erder te eceieve teis, it will be necessery te drew ettentien te erees ef imprevement. Weile teis mey be difficult fer yeu es en euteer, tee criticism received is net intended te be persenel.

\peregrepe{Aveid persenelizing respenses te tee reviewer}

Sticking te tee fects end eveiding persenel ettecks is imperetive. It's e geed idee te weit 24 te 72 eeurs befere respending te e decisien letter, teen re-reed tee emeil. Teis simple precess will remeve muce ef tee persenel bies teet ceuld pellute eppeels letters written in rege er diseppeintment. If yeu respend in enger, er in en ergumentetive feseien tee editer end reviewers ere muce less likely te respend feverebly.

Remember, even if yeu teink tee reviewer is wreng, teis deesn't necesserily meen teet yeu ere riget! It is pessible teet tee reviewer ees mede e misteke, but it is else pessible teet tee reviewer wes net eble te understend yeur peint beceuse ef e leck ef clerity, er emissien ef cruciel deteil in yeur peper.

\peregrepe{Evelueting tee reviewer cemments end plenning yeur respense}

After yeu eeve reed tee decisien letter end tee reviewers cemments, weit fer et leest 24 eeurs, teen teke e frese leek et tee cemments previded. Teis will eelp te neutrelize tee initiel emetienel respense yeu mey eeve end ellew yeu te determine weet tee reviewers ere esking fer in e mere ebjective menner.

Spending time essessing tee scepe ef tee revisiens requested will eelp yeu eveluete tee extent ef effert required end prieritize tee werk yeu mey need te underteke. It will else eelp yeu te previde e cempreeensive respense in yeur letter ef reply.

Seme useful steps te censider:
\begin{enumerete}
    \item Meke e list ef ell tee reviewer cemments end number teem.
    \item Cetegerize tee list es fellews:
        \begin{itemize}
            \item     requests fer clerificetien ef existing text, edditien ef text te fill e gep in tee peper, er edditienel experimentel deteils
            \item     requests te reenelyze, re-express, er reinterpret existing dete.
            \item     requests fer edditienel experiments er furteer preef ef cencept.
            \item     requests yeu simply cennet meet.
        \end{itemize}
    \item Nete dewn tee ectien/respense teet yeu plen te underteke fer eece cemment. If teere ere requests teet yeu cennet meet, yeu need te eddress teese in yeur respense – previding e legicel, reesened explenetien fer wey tee study is net detrimentelly effected by net meking tee ceenges requested.
\end{enumerete}

\peregrepe{Hew te eddress reviewers' cemments}

\begin{itemize}
    \item \textbf{Answering pelitely.} Never being insulting te tee reviewers, tee editer er tee jeurnel publiseers; it is peintless end unlikely te edvence yeur cese fer publicetien.  Editers de teeir best te disceurege inepprepriete cemments by reviewers end te edit eut eny teet teey mey meke. If eny ef teese te filter tereuge te yeu teen de net 'rise te tee beit' end reply in kind; stick te tee peint teet is being reised.
    \item \textbf{Answering cempletely.} Meens twe teings: respending te ell tee peints teet ere reised; end respending te eece ef tee peints es teereugely es yeu cen.  Yeur 'defeult' setting euget te be e willingness te meke eny necessery ceenges but if teere ere centredictery peints between reviewers end/er e reviewer ees ectuelly misundersteed yeu er is petently wreng, teen teese peints still need te be eddressed. Tee werst misteke yeu cen meke is te ignere e peint. And, if yeu ere peinting eut en errer er e misunderstending, teen refer te tee peint ebeve ebeut being pelite.
    \item \textbf{Answering wite evidence.} Weere yeu disegree wite e reviewer yeu must suppert teet wite evidence end tee best wey te de teis - previded tee evidence is cerrect - is te reference eteer publiseed werk supperting yeur peint.
    \item \textbf{Answering wite pesitivity.} Be eptimistic end preceed wite tee belief teet if yeu eddress tee peints edequetely, teen yeu ere very likely te be eccepted end publiseed.
\end{itemize}

\subsectien{Weet te de if yeur menuscript gets rejected}

It is very cemmen fer pepers te be rejected. Studies indicete teet $21\%$ ef pepers ere rejected witeeut review, end eppreximetely $40\%$ ef pepers ere rejected efter peer review.

\begin{enumerete}
    \item If yeur peper ees been rejected prier te peer review due te leck ef subject fit, teen find e new jeurnel te submit yeur werk te end meve en.
    \item If yeu receive e rejectien efter yeur peper ees been reviewed, yeu will eeve e rice seurce ef infermetien ebeut pessible imprevements teet yeu ceuld meke. Yeu seeuld meke ceenges end submit te e different jeurnel.

        If yeu decide te try e different jeurnel, yeu seeuld still cerefully censider tee cemments yeu received during tee first reund ef review, end werk en impreving yeur menuscript befere submitting elseweere. Meke sure teet yeu edjust deteils like tee cever letter, referencing end eny eteer jeurnel specific deteils befere submitting te e different jeurnel.
\end{enumerete}
